  <entry>
    <title>教你怎么免费搭建hexo博客</title>
    <url>/articles/%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAhexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="开始之前需要先阅读这篇文档"><a href="#开始之前需要先阅读这篇文档" class="headerlink" title="开始之前需要先阅读这篇文档"></a>开始之前需要先阅读这篇文档</h1><a href="/articles/Hexo%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.html" title="搭建Hexo博客前置条件 与 书写软件">搭建Hexo博客前置条件 与 书写软件</a>

<h2 id="1-安装-执行前先安装nodejs"><a href="#1-安装-执行前先安装nodejs" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装 执行前先安装nodejs"></a>1. 安装 执行前先安装nodejs</h2><p>随便找一个目录 打开控制台(cmd)</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="2-创建并运行hexo"><a href="#2-创建并运行hexo" class="headerlink" title="2. 创建并运行hexo"></a>2. 创建并运行hexo</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init &lt;项目文件夹名称&gt;</span><br><span class="line">cd &lt;项目文件夹名称&gt;</span><br><span class="line">hexo serve</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="3-修改-config-yml"><a href="#3-修改-config-yml" class="headerlink" title="3. 修改 _config.yml"></a>3. 修改 _config.yml</h2><p>修改标题 作者等信息</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Site</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">他的博客</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">''</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">''</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 搜索引擎关键字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">keywords:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">他是谁</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 指定语言为简体中文</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-Hans</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 指定时区为中国</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span> <span class="string">'Asia/Shanghai'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="4-安装主题（可选）"><a href="#4-安装主题（可选）" class="headerlink" title="4. 安装主题（可选）"></a>4. 安装主题（可选）</h2><p>这边推荐next</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -s https://api.github.com/repos/iissnan/hexo-theme-next/releases/latest | grep tarball_url | cut -d '"' -f 4 | wget -i - -O- | tar -zx -C themes/next --strip-components=1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 清理文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 启动服务 启动后会自动编译</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo serve</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="5-新建文章"><a href="#5-新建文章" class="headerlink" title="5. 新建文章"></a>5. 新建文章</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new post '今天天气真好'</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后hexo就会在 source/_posts 下面 新建一个 markdom 文件 今天天气真好.md</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- 文章标题 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">title: 今天天气真好 </span><br><span class="line">date: 2020-04-16 16:28:16</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">在这里输入正文</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>新建后直接刷新浏览器如果看不到效果</p>
<p>需要ctrl+c停止 hexo serve </p>
<p>然后再执行 一遍 就好了</p>
<h2 id="6-部署服务器"><a href="#6-部署服务器" class="headerlink" title="6. 部署服务器"></a>6. 部署服务器</h2><h3 id="1-首先需要注册一个码云账号-https-gitee-com"><a href="#1-首先需要注册一个码云账号-https-gitee-com" class="headerlink" title="1. 首先需要注册一个码云账号 https://gitee.com/"></a>1. 首先需要注册一个码云账号 <a href="https://gitee.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://gitee.com/</a></h3><h3 id="2-新建一个仓库"><a href="#2-新建一个仓库" class="headerlink" title="2. 新建一个仓库"></a>2. 新建一个仓库</h3><p>开源-&gt;勾选上公开<br><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/04/16/s4ATtfIQpekY3iM.png" alt="新建仓库.png"></p>
<h3 id="3-修改-config-yml-1"><a href="#3-修改-config-yml-1" class="headerlink" title="3. 修改_config.yml"></a>3. 修改_config.yml</h3><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/04/16/ymDl6AubikQo3JI.png" alt="image.png"></p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: #你的git仓库地址</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">.....</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> URL</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment"># If your site is put in a subdirectory, set url as 'http://yoursite.com/child' and root as '/child/'</span></span></span><br><span class="line">url: https://&lt;码云英文账户名&gt;.gitee.io/&lt;博客项目名&gt;/</span><br><span class="line">root: /&lt;博客项目名&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="4-执行命令上传编译后的代码到仓库"><a href="#4-执行命令上传编译后的代码到仓库" class="headerlink" title="4. 执行命令上传编译后的代码到仓库"></a>4. 执行命令上传编译后的代码到仓库</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="5-开启码云的-gitee-pages服务-部署访问"><a href="#5-开启码云的-gitee-pages服务-部署访问" class="headerlink" title="5. 开启码云的 gitee pages服务 部署访问"></a>5. 开启码云的 gitee pages服务 部署访问</h3><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/04/16/uFwm9iSDsBhb2xL.png" alt="image.png"></p>
<p>点击部署 骚等片刻 你的博客就部署好了<br><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/04/16/FIpLGhRAy2d5NSj.png" alt="image.png"></p>
<p>访问地址格式为<br>https://&lt;码云英文账户名&gt;.gitee.io/&lt;博客项目名&gt;/</p>
]]></content>
